<item>
            <title>[LU-18146] Refresh SUSE 15 SP4 and SP5 ldiskfs series</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18146</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Recent ldiskfs fixes cause the linux-5.14/ext4-prealloc.patch to no longer apply to SUSE 15 SP4/5.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;SP4/5 are also missing the recent encryption and commit speedup fixes.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;With the series fixed IGET_NO_CHECKS is also needed to build sp4/sp4.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
